{"tid":1379301,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「重要」請將催淚彈交比滅煙隊伍處理","createTime":"2019-07-28T18:32:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T14:02:16.000Z","uid":16461,"like":80,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"9b5f42dd02fb02017c17a4a272cc849c5169bad2","tid":1379301,"uid":16461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T18:32:53.000Z","msg":"發夢見到現場好多義士都預備左水筒/水壺做滅煙工作，但每次有催淚彈都十分混亂，大家十幾支水一齊淋浪費極多嘅水源，甚至撞開左滅煙隊伍嘅義士<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">如果下次前線見到有催淚彈落到身邊，請散開交比滅煙隊伍，佢地好快就會跑去處理催淚彈，唔好再用過量水源滅煙！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n請廣傳！"},{"pid":"7340c2aa3c1a14a5a31dc0a8eff78a55f3a556bf","tid":1379301,"uid":263161,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T18:33:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4d9f6f90a34ee05cfebb4befc55917afb8e68949","tid":1379301,"uid":16461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T18:33:38.000Z","msg":"光復香港，時代革命"},{"pid":"30f7d87622a12068c04200bb4edd63962c8e5def","tid":1379301,"uid":16461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T18:34:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c7f3a270ba9cce94b50502647e67138a571f84ff","tid":1379301,"uid":272196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T18:34:52.000Z","msg":"光復香港  時代革命"},{"pid":"265b5cfb109936775069d31173f6f5a438a69f08","tid":1379301,"uid":117636,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T18:35:38.000Z","msg":"咁有冇加入方式？"},{"pid":"b832b773bce628121285c13906dbda9446f3254e","tid":1379301,"uid":146865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T18:37:20.000Z","msg":"［推上熱門］推翻暴政就係需要不斷地進化<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1379151\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1379151</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n幫手推小弟感激不盡🙇🏻&zwj;♂️🙇🏻&zwj;♂️"},{"pid":"0952c40d364833b1cc7e890ffff9fbdda7bde90e","tid":1379301,"uid":251119,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T18:38:32.000Z","msg":"建議參考first aid做法<br />\n定一個統一既標誌分清滅煙隊<br />\n有煙既時候 即刻讓路同比水滅煙隊<br />\n咁樣有效過全民滅煙"},{"pid":"5f286772417048b470407f9b0f90c7d4a5851fb4","tid":1379301,"uid":293036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T18:40:55.000Z","msg":"分工真係好重要 大家要冷靜唔好亂"},{"pid":"b044fd16b1509e345f7a74ef971117a7c90afb5e","tid":1379301,"uid":16461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T18:46:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d19db6dc04144d49ace6df0de85876e42124c5e1","tid":1379301,"uid":36467,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T18:48:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8303b63b9b463c0380255e8ac19de5de64b548d2","tid":1379301,"uid":16461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"265b5cfb109936775069d31173f6f5a438a69f08","tid":1379301,"uid":117636,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T18:35:38.000Z","msg":"咁有冇加入方式？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T18:49:09.000Z","msg":"有筒、燒桿手套，每個都係滅煙隊伍<br />\n<br />\n有巴打提儀喺用First Aid方式黎分，係有效，但因為滅煙隊伍唔似First Aid，就算啲狗見到都照打照捉，同一批人好危險"},{"pid":"78e71bb6676bd037ea89cde70268aaf6218c737f","tid":1379301,"uid":16461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d19db6dc04144d49ace6df0de85876e42124c5e1","tid":1379301,"uid":36467,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T18:48:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T18:49:57.000Z","msg":"謝義士！"},{"pid":"482b0ec65d8553a05c661373968d2f222ba61751","tid":1379301,"uid":16461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T18:50:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"55c65ae07c8d087434d3007e1d316391ff379993","tid":1379301,"uid":16461,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0952c40d364833b1cc7e890ffff9fbdda7bde90e","tid":1379301,"uid":251119,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T18:38:32.000Z","msg":"建議參考first aid做法<br />\n定一個統一既標誌分清滅煙隊<br />\n有煙既時候 即刻讓路同比水滅煙隊<br />\n咁樣有效過全民滅煙"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T18:51:00.000Z","msg":"用First Aid方式黎分，係有效，但因為滅煙隊伍唔似First Aid，就算啲狗見到都照打照捉，同一批人好危險"},{"pid":"2c80131653649addf2754485e190ae2752971e34","tid":1379301,"uid":216426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T18:51:14.000Z","msg":"求大家幫手推 小弟得一對手<br />\n<br />\n雙普選比獨立調查更重要<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1379266\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1379266</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"bbf3cc4cf15795ba0511e8dd0994d4f4e052cd58","tid":1379301,"uid":57771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T18:52:01.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"84824e0a5ee9a7ebe94638c8cefeb009000f2ad7","tid":1379301,"uid":50252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T18:55:29.000Z","msg":"作為一個單車撚<br />\n入山單車手套濕水就可以<br />\n有D仲可以用到艾瘋TIM<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個日踩單有仆街放煙 我執起就掉佢老母<br />\n執返半打左右 就再去濕濕佢<br />\n<br />\n真係唔好拎兩支水仔就狗衝 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05157b1cf9676294869a3c6bc671f8b92e8e5d37","tid":1379301,"uid":16461,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T18:57:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"068720bcdd6ae4b600c11a6df5999ed158ab5a0f","tid":1379301,"uid":21275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T18:58:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"af376f452449b6016ffce34a0e0f21b2596b50d4","tid":1379301,"uid":80139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T19:00:29.000Z","msg":"支持公務員罷工"},{"pid":"bfada273f291d01c25b3a343c301ce4763a62cb3","tid":1379301,"uid":145296,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T19:01:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ed7dabb3f987c5f67c5377eb8371c5b76698c3d","tid":1379301,"uid":16461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bfada273f291d01c2